Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,contenders from the New World.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.05,0:04:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujitora?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you help him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.89,0:04:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to stop you right there,\NHeavenly Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.46,0:04:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...arrest him, not to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.73,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you seem quite curious about\Nthat "complication" that I mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna hear about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.25,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Decisive Battle!\NGiolla vs. the Straw Hats!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.17,0:05:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NIt goes back 800 years, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 kings from 20 countries came together
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.56,0:05:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nat the center of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and formed one giant organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we call\Nthe World Government now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kings who created it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...decided to move to the \NHoly land of Marie Jois
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand live there with their families.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nefeltari Family of Alabasta refused,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso there were 19 families to be exact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:06:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The descendents of those \Ncreators who still live there
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.71,0:06:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and reign over the world \Nare the Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means, however, that those
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,19 countries lost their royal \Nfamilies 800 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.97,0:06:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you following?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.11,0:06:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In those countries, they elected \Nnew kings out of necessity
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand new royal families rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the case of my country - Dressrosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe new royalty was the Riku Family.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the old royalty who moved to the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.88,0:06:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holyland of Marie Jois as the \Ncreators of the world were
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Don Quixote Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:07:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great music and the art of the sea, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.85,0:07:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know art, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NDon't tell me you're going to Green Bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law would be stunned!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I come to pick up Caesar,\Nnot you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook is acting strange!\NAre you gonna turn around on us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.52,0:07:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone-kichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.51,0:07:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call yourself a swordsman\Nbut betray your friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just realized something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an artist after all! \NI'm living to create!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dead though!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.36,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These ordinary people can't \Nunderstand, Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than anything, we \Nwant to express ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.45,0:07:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThey don't understand that kind of passion!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an art of life! Dying Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.83,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing, Giolla-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.37,0:07:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.91,0:07:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't be more excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I represented the tragedy of \NDressrosa quite exquisitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.89,0:08:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In 10 minutes or so, \Nthese annoying kids will
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.73,0:08:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,become part of the art completely
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.29,0:08:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and choke to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.06,0:08:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone-kichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you how impressed I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.48,0:08:19.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NLet me play a song to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind doing so, Soul King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.45,0:08:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So could you turn my violin \Nand bow back, Giolla-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.39,0:08:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Take it away, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.29,0:08:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.69,0:08:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not... suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost unconscious...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this, Giolla-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nthis bow is actually a cane sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, uh-huh, play nice music for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:08:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I cut you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.87,0:09:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Painting Song Bamboo Flute Slice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.81,0:09:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,PAINTING SONG BAMBOO FLUTE SLICE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,JOINT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but I don't understand \Nart after all because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.25,0:09:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,KNOTHOLE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.10,0:09:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are like knotholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.69,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bone-kichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started to worry\Nabout Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} before you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I know she wants me\Nto come instead of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.64,0:09:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon, this is a map to the \NToy House where your friend is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you get to see Luffy,\Ncontact the Sunny with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check to see what everybody is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay on the Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.43,0:10:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how can we reach Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I knew how,\Nwe wouldn't be standing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place is all closed up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't see anybody to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.15,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should not make a bold move.\NI almost got caught earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.75,0:10:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then should I just chop up the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.74,0:10:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I call a bold move!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can slice it gently instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point! Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.87,0:10:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We have to be careful!\N--How do you want me to cut it then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.81,0:10:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's "Pirate Hunter" Zoro-senpai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say he chopped up 100 men\Nin Whisky Peak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and rampaged through Enies Lobby!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Three-Sword Style swordsman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.22,0:11:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's always supporting the Straw Hats\Nas Luffy-senpai's right-hand man{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and is considered vice captain!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's so cool!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh? Why am I crying? Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro-{\i1}senpai{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.84,0:11:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Go, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.92,0:11:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! Way to go!\NShe made another guy drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.02,0:11:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go! Whew! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.64,0:11:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's getting really excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.68,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to be back to myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.17,0:11:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NThanks, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did great, Bone-kichi.\NYou made me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought I was \Ngonna die at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not that big a deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.99,0:12:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it is a very big deal! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.73,0:12:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a sleep-in-your-lap party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of party is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.22,0:12:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,handcuff her, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.71,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna touch those.\NThey drain my energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.68,0:12:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining and just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.86,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who hasn't \Neaten a Devil Fruit here
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso why don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said "Do it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh boy, oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.15,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul King! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got fooled completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were connected \Nto each other because we're
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.13,0:12:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both artists and I dropped my guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are such imprudent people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.04,0:13:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna imprint my \Nultimate art on your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.25,0:13:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and send you off to heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,G-Giolla-{\i1}san{\i0}... R-Relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heaven's Door Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.94,0:13:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What the hell?!\N--What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.66,0:14:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the pinnacle of artistry -\NHeaven's Door Art!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how beautiful this world of art is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys should be happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you can die\Nseeing the most
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,beautiful thing in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.88,0:15:17.50,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,DRESSROSA - THE PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gladius, why don't you cool down\Na little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.95,0:15:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see how badly
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that woman's betrayal\Nupsets our plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.08,0:15:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The plan was simple: that woman, Violet,\Ncaptures "Black Foot" Sanji
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.20,0:15:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks into his mind\Nto see all of their strategies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, we could foil all of their plans\Nand kill them all one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what did she do instead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NShe beat up her own men and ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.50,0:15:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not gonna explode here, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I despise and wish death \Nupon people who aren't
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.31,0:16:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,punctual and who can't follow a plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:27.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,GLADIUS\NTHE DON QUIXOTE FAMILY (THE PICA ARMY)
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's worse, she betrayed us - I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.15,0:16:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Young Master. I'm not gonna \Nlet her get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violet was acting strange from last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:50.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With her Clairvoyance, she could've found\Nthe Straw Hat's ship yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.88,0:16:57.43,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,NORTHEAST DRESSROSA\NIN THE DIRECTION OF GREEN BIT
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.45,0:17:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're not supposed\Nto be here, Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.95,0:17:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wait at the harbor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy soldiers are\Neverywhere at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and your friends may want to\Nchange your rendezvous point.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.37,0:17:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The Navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are four Navy ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.67,0:17:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least three thousand Navy soldiers\Nare here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.61,0:17:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found out all of that alone\Nin that short amount of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of my abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clairvoyance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this power, I can see \Nthings within a 4000km
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,diameter as from a bird's point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.61,0:18:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see everything that's \Ngoing in this country from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.33,0:18:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have to worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They can't catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, are you gonna stay in this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.61,0:18:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm gonna do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Violet-{\i1}chan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find your ship anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?! Hey!\NWhat should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.14,0:18:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can {\i1}we{\i0} do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've no choice but to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.37,0:19:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weather Egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come hatch, thunder-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.38,0:19:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.00,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your technique is not very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For these kinds of things, I would do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.00,0:19:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this, to accentuate its beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.72,0:19:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.14,0:19:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you excuse me\Nfor cutting you, Giolla-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.47,0:20:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Heaven's Door Art is imbued with my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nfor pursuing ultimate beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest beauty is the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.32,0:20:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cola barrels have been set!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.69,0:20:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Sunny's source of power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWith that, we can fire the Gaon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.41,0:20:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gaon Cannon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly,\NI put a target in the circle with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish Usopp were here\Nbut the target is big so I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook! It's ready!\NGet out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Gaon Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.61,0:21:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!\NI'm not gonna let you get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Just how tough is she?!\N--She just won't go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.38,0:22:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go all out now!\NYou pissed me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, who wants to die first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.21,0:22:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You damn brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Momo-{\i1}chan{\i0}, move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What's wrong?\N--It's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.53,0:22:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ship emerged out of nowhere\Nand it's been hit by lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.47,0:22:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, lightning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Who did you call Ms. Mermaid...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.18,0:23:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You did it, Momonosuke!\N--Yes, I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
